<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659842>
    dc:description "FIGS. 203–208. Rhagovelia papuensis group, female ventral abdomen showing locations of depressions and patterns of setiferation. 203. Rhagovelia loriae n. sp.; specimen from New Guinea, Dorobisoro, CL 7260. 204. Rhagovelia guiagoila n. sp.; specimen from Basilaki Is., Kalawai River, CL 7294. 205. Rhagovelia basima n. sp.; specimen from Fergusson Is., Yaya River, CL 7178. 206. Rhagovelia elongata n. sp.; specimen from Goodenough Is., Matalamoia River, CL 7187. 207. Rhagovelia bwagabwaga n. sp.; specimen from Misima Is., Keyana Creek, CL 7206. 208. Rhagovelia priori n. sp.; specimen from New Guinea, Kofure River, CL 7304." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659842/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659858>
    dc:description "FIGS. 234–238. Rhagovelia bwagabwaga n. sp., structural details; specimens from Misima Is., Keyana Creek, CL 7206. 234. Wingless male, dorsal habitus. 235. Wingless female, dorsal habitus. 236. Male right hind leg, dorsal view. 237. Male left paramere, outer lateral view. 238. Male proctiger, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659858/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659860>
    dc:description "FIG. 239. Keyana Creek, Misima Is., Milne Bay Province, Papua New Guinea, CL 7206, type-locality for R. bwagabwaga n. sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659860/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659862>
    dc:description "FIG. 240. Distributions of species in the R. yela subgroup in the Louisiade Islands, and R. suloga on Woodlark Island." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659862/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

